title: Duplex
typeOfFood: Lacto, International, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Grand open Aug 1, 2014 a cafe and bar. The cafe on the ground floor offers some vegetarian dishes with also raw and vegan choices. Happy hour daily 4-7pm. Upstairs on the first floor is the bar which is open til 2am.
